formally introduced.

36:55.204 --> 36:56.339
Mr. Werner.

36:57.240 --> 36:58.707
- Mr. Wayne.
- I know,

36:58.709 --> 37:00.077
I heard the name on stage.

37:01.545 --> 37:05.480
Congratulations are in order
on account of your triumph,

37:05.482 --> 37:06.882
you insensitive critter.

37:08.051 --> 37:09.685
You've misinterpreted
the situation.

37:09.687 --> 37:11.319
I saw you harass
her with my own eyes.

37:11.321 --> 37:12.253
I did nothing of the sort.

37:12.255 --> 37:13.655
Are you calling me a liar?

37:13.657 --> 37:15.827
Mr. Wayne is my
chaperone for the evening.

37:21.099 --> 37:22.700
You must understand

37:24.435 --> 37:26.671
