in being alone,

37:27.872 --> 37:32.308
especially one such as
I, the physical beast

37:32.310 --> 37:33.812
that I am burdened with being.

37:38.316 --> 37:41.085
It is no beast of
burden, Frau Honey.

37:43.555 --> 37:44.389
Really?

37:45.825 --> 37:46.658
Hmm.

37:47.992 --> 37:50.863
Please refrain from
calling me Frau, won't you?

37:51.798 --> 37:54.030
In the absence of my beloved

37:54.032 --> 37:56.133
I've rather reverted
to Fraulein.

37:56.135 --> 37:57.668
Oh.

37:57.670 --> 38:00.937
Fraulein Honey, a German
weiner-schnitzel correctly prepared

38:00.939 --> 38:04.075
and consumed offers
unparalleled levels of comfort.

38:04.077 --> 38:05.909
I remain, as ever,
in your service.

38:05.911 --> 38:08.044
Hmm, what a
fascinating proposition.

38:08.046 --> 38:09.547
Yeah.

38:09.549 --> 38:12.583
I find myself without the
appetite this evening however.

38:12.585 --> 38:14.084
Mr. Wayne and I are
rather building up

38:14.086 --> 38:16.254
to a moment of passion.

38:16.256 --> 38:18.990
Surely, a prerequisite
of the evening.

38:18.992 --> 38:22.093
(GIGGLING)

38:22.095 --> 38:23.261
(MR. WERNER SPEAKING
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE)

38:23.263 --> 38:25.596
How very cultured a chaperone.

38:25.598 --> 38:27.666
Sex as a prerequisite.

38:27.668 --> 38:28.600
(GIGGLING)

38:28.602 --> 38:29.437
Mr. Werner, please.

38:30.704 --> 38:33.070
(GIGGLING)

38:33.072 --> 38:34.273
What filth.

38:34.275 --> 38:36.108
Oh, Mein Fuhrer will
positively rejoice

38:36.110 --> 38:38.310
