of such etiquette.

38:38.312 --> 38:40.713
As so I am currently rejoicing.

38:40.715 --> 38:43.751
Romance is not his forte.

38:44.919 --> 38:48.924
("NAZI ROCK" BY
SERGE GAINSBOURG)

38:52.627 --> 38:56.964
