(FESTIVE MUSIC)

39:16.752 --> 39:17.685
Huzzah!

39:17.687 --> 39:19.854
[SHOEROPE] Commissioner.

39:19.856 --> 39:22.556
(OLD WEST THEME MUSIC)

39:22.558 --> 39:24.325
So there he is.

39:24.327 --> 39:26.596
